## Command to enable git in a directory/folder

git init

## Command to stage changes

git add filename

## Command to commit changes

git commit -m "Message here"

## Command to check status of current working tree

git status

## Command to list all the commits

git log

## Command to push the local commit to remote

git push

git push --set-upstream origin master

## Command to create new branch

git checkout -b branchName

## Command to switch to another branch
git checkout branchName

## Command to clone a repository
git clone https://github.com/vaaluvishnu5146/LearningGit.git
